cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SY

This paper discusses the cost and efficiency of wireless networks, which is closely related to the field of network infrastructure (cs.NI). The use of coding to improve goodput is a topic in information theory (cs.IT), and the paper also discusses the resilience of protocols to network failures (cs.CR). The optimization of network resources is a topic in distributed computing (cs.DC), and the paper proposes a solution to improve network efficiency. Finally, the paper discusses the impact of improving network efficiency on network providers, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY).
